snippet.title: Settlements Rising Gameplay | Release Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Settlements Rising is a medieval city builder, colony simulator game, and will be released in early access on 2 October 2024.

Wishlist the game: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2378910?utm_source=youtubetrailer2
